<TEXT>
employees of a grocery store are losing 
patience with the continuing escapades of a squirrel that has taken 
up residence amid the coffee cakes doughnuts and hot dog rolls 
the critter has run up a 25 tab at the farm fare iga over the 
last two weeks 
employees took to shooing the squirrel outside but it keeps 
coming back 
it was a joke the first couple of times but now he is 
beginning to be a problem said store manager dick emery 
the squirrel once jumped over a womans shoulder as she reached 
for a box of rice leaving her shrieking as it hightailed it up 
the aisle 
i came in one morning and there he was just sitting down on 
top of the wine coolers in the front of the store emery said 
it was almost as if he was waiting for the chase to begin 
fritz sabbow executive director of the local humane society 
said the only way to catch the squirrel will be with a net and it 
wont be easy they are pretty quick 
