for a while it looked like the good old days 
with takeovers defensive alliances and stock rumors coming one 
after another two phone giants merging a french hotelier buying 
an american budget motel chain two technology companies forming a 
strategic joint venture 
there even was wild speculation that mitsubishi group the 
